          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is a kind of manual and is a compendium of different rites and the rules and regulations governing them, to be used by a priest or senior householder for performing ceremonies to mark the completion of the twelfth day of the half month. Such rites as the removal of sins are invoked.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
